<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            color: #2F3B40;
            background-color: #f0fdf4; /* 사이트의 연한 녹색 배경 */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        .subscription-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .logo-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center; /* 로고 중앙 정렬 */
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2F3B40;
        }
        .form-label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #0F172A;
        }
        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .form-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #54B435;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(84, 180, 53, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #54B435;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #469b2d;
        }
        /* 커스텀 체크박스 스타일 */
        .custom-checkbox {
            appearance: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            height: 1.25rem;
            width: 1.25rem;
            min-width: 1.25rem;
            border: 2px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            top: 2px;
        }
        .custom-checkbox:checked {
            background-color: #54B435;
            border-color: #54B435;
        }
        .custom-checkbox:checked::after {
            content: '✔';
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: white;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            line-height: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="subscription-card">
        <div class="logo-header">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center">
                <img src="/images/unique-mark.png" alt="유니크 특허법률사무소 로고" class="h-8 mr-3">
                <span class="logo-text">유니크 특허법률사무소</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-2 text-center">IP 라운지</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#2F3B40] mb-6 text-center">유니크 특허사무소 뉴스레터</p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            안녕하세요. 유니크 특허사무소의 이준혁변리사입니다.<br>
            IP 라운지에는 특허와 상표에 관련된 정보나 전략을 소개하기도 하고, 트랜디한 투자/시장 정보에 특허 분석을 더한 지식재산 뉴스를 담고 있습니다.<br>
            <strong class="font-bold text-gray-800">아래 정보 입력 후, 꼭 "구독 신청" 버튼을 눌러주세요,</strong> 감사합니다.
        </p>

        <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="dd3c9ad5-1802-4bd1-b7e6-397002308afa">
            <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value=""https://unicpat.com/thanks"">
            <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="[유니크] 뉴스레터 구독 신청이 도착했습니다.">
            <input type="hidden" name="from_site" value="유니크 뉴스레터 구독 페이지">

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">이름 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-input" required>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label for="company" class="form-label">회사명</label>
                    <input type="text" id="company" name="company_name" class="form-input">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">이메일 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-input" required>
                </div>

                <div class="border-t pt-6">
                    <label class="form-label">수신 항목 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                    <div class="flex items-center mt-2">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="newsletter-check" name="subscription_list" value="Newsletter" class="custom-checkbox" checked required>
                        <label for="newsletter-check" class="text-gray-700">뉴스레터</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="form-label">개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                    <div class="flex items-center mt-2">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="privacy-consent" name="privacy_consent" value="Agreed" class="custom-checkbox" required>
                        <label for="privacy-consent" class="text-gray-700">동의함</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">구독 신청</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>